node.text:
$7.995 Million
2.2 Acres | 4 Bed | 6 Bath | 7 Car Garage + Lift

A Bold & Innovative Newly Built Estate, 15 Provence Court Is An Ultra-Luxe, Architectural Masterpiece Offering Inimitable Style, Scale, & Exquisite Design On Over 2 Acres. The Estate Boasts 4 Bedrooms, 6 Bathrooms, Including Dual Garages That Can House Up To 8 Cars. Surrounded By Magnificent Views, & Inspiring Quality, Residents Will Be Immersed In An Environment Of Creativity And Luxury. Welcome To A Truly Bespoke Lifestyle - A Once In A Lifetime Offering!

Visit 15PROVENCE.COM for more details.

Ramin Khaze @khaze.re

node.text:
What do you think about this home?

This modern home was planned with one main goal: to celebrate its surrounding beauty. No matter where you find yourselves in the house, you can experience the views of the endless blue ocean, the lush green vegetation and the unique white sand.

The emphasis has been placed on the transitions between the interior and exterior living environments, which has been a primary feature of Caymanian homes for decades.

The house is designed by @trio_architecture and is located in Grand Cayman, Cayman Islands Photos by @rmstudiocorp.
🤝 @restless.arch

node.text:
Hugo Suissas @suissas is a self-taught #Lisbon-based #photographer who proves that you can make any photo much more interesting by trying out a different #perspective. He turns simple bridges and landscapes into surreal and fantastical places, and items like keys, fruits, and kids' toys into magical props.
📸 @suissas

node.text:
Share your thoughts about this design?

Designed by Indian architecture and interior design firm Loop Design Studio @loopdesignstudio Playground is a #restaurant and lounge located in the main commercial hub of Chandigarh, India. It is an energetic injection of multiple textures, color and materiality that comes together on a beautiful canvas.

Photography: Purnesh Dev Nikhanj @purneshdev 
🤝 @amazing.architecture
